1513
02:17:15,255 --> 02:17:17,240
Looks like you know this place.

1514
02:17:17,985 --> 02:17:19,184
What's the use in hiding from you?

1515
02:17:20,558 --> 02:17:23,024
Our business started from here.

1516
02:17:23,872 --> 02:17:27,683
And this is the place where
death touched us and left.

1517
02:17:28,185 --> 02:17:31,792
There was a scoundrel
Major Vijay Malhotra.

1518
02:17:33,282 --> 02:17:35,877
He thought he was the
protector of the nation!

1519
02:17:36,615 --> 02:17:37,717
He caught us.

1520
02:17:38,381 --> 02:17:42,290
If DK hadn't reached in time,
he would have killed all of us.

1521
02:17:43,317 --> 02:17:45,360
That dog was very strong!

1522
02:17:46,365 --> 02:17:48,269
But fate was with us.

1523
02:17:49,091 --> 02:17:51,526
We gave that scoundrel such a death!

1524
02:17:52,570 --> 02:17:54,141
That it's quoted as an example.

1525
02:17:54,818 --> 02:17:56,038
What did you do?

1526
02:17:56,570 --> 02:17:58,620
We proved the martyr a traitor.

1527
02:17:59,378 --> 02:18:01,620
We didn't let him be cremated!

1528
02:18:05,193 --> 02:18:08,501
Some will die today too.
But won't be cremated.

1529
02:18:09,081 --> 02:18:11,987
Of DK and his men!

1530
02:18:19,949 --> 02:18:20,824
Why did you stop the car?

1531
02:18:26,876 --> 02:18:29,808
A goddess is sitting in
this temple since 20 years.

1532
02:18:31,070 --> 02:18:35,637
They say anyone who sees her
gets his wishes fulfilled.

1533
02:18:37,225 --> 02:18:38,535
Let's go see her.

1534
02:18:41,540 --> 02:18:43,219
I will definitely see her.

1535
02:18:44,142 --> 02:18:46,954
So that I can see DK's corpse very soon.

1536
02:20:04,384 --> 02:20:08,352
For 20 years these eyes have only
seen hatred and been shunned.

1537
02:20:10,103 --> 02:20:11,659
I have seen them everyday.

1538
02:20:13,807 --> 02:20:14,381
But...

1539
02:20:17,615 --> 02:20:23,509
for the first time,
I'm seeing eyes filled with tears.

1540
02:20:26,220 --> 02:20:26,883
Raju.

1541
02:20:29,749 --> 02:20:30,296
Mother!

1542
02:20:30,926 --> 02:20:31,849
Raju.

1543
02:20:34,254 --> 02:20:36,424
- Raju.
- Mother.

1544
02:20:38,202 --> 02:20:40,931
I kept you away for 20 years!

1545
02:20:42,269 --> 02:20:46,744
Despite being a mother,
I didn't give you that love.

1546
02:20:48,612 --> 02:20:51,559
Forgive me!

1547
02:20:51,679 --> 02:20:53,839
Forgive me!

1548
02:20:53,944 --> 02:20:56,794
No, you were not away from me.

1549
02:20:57,754 --> 02:21:04,017
The dust of your feet was
always with me like a blessing.

1550
02:21:06,807 --> 02:21:11,629
Now it's time for your wait
and my pledge to be fulfilled.

1551
02:21:12,853 --> 02:21:15,406
See whom I've brought here!

1552
02:21:29,978 --> 02:21:31,954
'Your mother and son can't stay here!'

1553
02:21:32,420 --> 02:21:36,461
'She won't leave like this.
We'll put such a stigma on her forehead'

1554
02:21:36,575 --> 02:21:38,289
'that she won't be able to face anyone!'

1555
02:21:38,329 --> 02:21:41,814
- 'Throw him out!
- Yes, throw him out!'

1556
02:21:48,546 --> 02:21:51,603
Leave my child!

1557
02:21:52,340 --> 02:21:54,529
Leave my child!

1558
02:21:57,695 --> 02:22:00,416
No! No! No!!!

1559
02:22:07,032 --> 02:22:09,814
'My husband is a traitor'

1560
02:22:10,528 --> 02:22:11,112
Geeta!

1561
02:22:13,523 --> 02:22:15,140
I'm the son of this goddess!

1562
02:22:18,188 --> 02:22:19,369
This is that goddess

1563
02:22:20,382 --> 02:22:24,574
of whose forehead you wrote
the stigma of shame, not pride!

1564
02:22:25,850 --> 02:22:27,672
I'm the son of Vijay Malhotra

1565
02:22:28,548 --> 02:22:31,691
who was called a traitor
despite being a martyr!

1566
02:22:32,967 --> 02:22:34,699
Do you know why I brought you here?

1567
02:22:35,799 --> 02:22:39,123
So that the soul where the
greatest injustice was done

1568
02:22:40,652 --> 02:22:42,593
justice too should be given there!

1569
02:22:44,306 --> 02:22:47,870
And my mother who has been
doing penance in this wilderness

1570
02:22:49,055 --> 02:22:51,445
can see justice being done!

1571
02:22:56,171 --> 02:22:58,280
Traitor!

1572
02:23:13,076 --> 02:23:18,117
People die but their voice don't!

1573
02:23:20,142 --> 02:23:21,821
Listen!

1574
02:23:22,641 --> 02:23:28,633
Listen to the voice of my dad's
torture in this sand!

1575
02:23:29,124 --> 02:23:30,439
Listen!

1576
02:23:36,345 --> 02:23:40,886
Listen to a child cry
and weep for his dad!

1577
02:23:42,177 --> 02:23:47,749
Hear the scream of a mother looking
for her husband's body in a storm!

1578
02:23:48,090 --> 02:23:52,242
Hear my mother's screams!

1579
02:23:55,407 --> 02:23:58,901
Listen!

1580
02:24:01,450 --> 02:24:03,214
Hear my mother's screams!

1581
02:24:16,287 --> 02:24:16,976
DK.

1582
02:24:21,832 --> 02:24:23,734
Not DK but Jaswant.

1583
02:24:24,206 --> 02:24:24,701
Remove.

1584
02:24:28,489 --> 02:24:29,096
Jaswant.

1585
02:24:29,546 --> 02:24:31,354
I recognized you earlier itself.

1586
02:24:31,706 --> 02:24:35,352
You haven't come here
but been brought here.

1587
02:24:36,124 --> 02:24:39,859
According to Raju's plan I
informed you of Pratap's arrival.

1588
02:24:40,338 --> 02:24:41,708
I released you on purpose.

1589
02:24:42,478 --> 02:24:47,082
Because we know you would come
here to save him for your business.

1590
02:24:47,794 --> 02:24:51,087
And since Jaswant has
been forgiven by the law

1591
02:24:51,557 --> 02:24:55,129
you'll be tried as DK not Jaswant!

1592
02:24:55,902 --> 02:24:59,599
You cheated your partners
for their shares.

1593
02:24:59,788 --> 02:25:00,371
Not us.

1594
02:25:01,921 --> 02:25:03,251
You are under arrest.

1595
02:25:33,122 --> 02:25:34,522
Raju!

1596
02:25:37,605 --> 02:25:41,662
What did you think I'd
come alone to save my man?

1597
02:25:42,993 --> 02:25:43,935
Raju!

1598
02:25:47,002 --> 02:25:48,488
- Raju!
- Mother!

1599
02:25:49,429 --> 02:25:49,949
Mother!

1600
02:25:51,194 --> 02:25:52,634
Mother!

1601
02:25:58,685 --> 02:25:59,188
Mother!

1602
02:26:03,757 --> 02:26:06,862
Wanted me to hear screams?

1603
02:26:06,938 --> 02:26:09,308
Now you scream!

1604
02:26:09,454 --> 02:26:10,942
No! Raju!

1605
02:26:11,583 --> 02:26:12,450
Leave him.

1606
02:26:17,333 --> 02:26:18,091
Mother!

1607
02:26:19,291 --> 02:26:22,136
- Mother!
- Raju!

1608
02:26:22,160 --> 02:26:25,883
- Mother!
- Beat him!

1609
02:26:26,326 --> 02:26:27,263
Raju!

1610
02:26:27,674 --> 02:26:29,018
Mother!

1611
02:26:30,042 --> 02:26:31,688
Raju!

1612
02:26:32,634 --> 02:26:34,606
- Mother!
- Raju!

1613
02:26:35,531 --> 02:26:38,416
Mother! Mother!

1614
02:26:38,779 --> 02:26:40,665
Raju!

1615
02:26:45,132 --> 02:26:46,470
Raju!

1616
02:26:57,293 --> 02:27:00,691
This rascal is Vijay Malhotra's son.

1617
02:27:01,584 --> 02:27:03,548
His dad was buried here after his death.

1618
02:27:04,529 --> 02:27:05,430
Bury him alive!

1619
02:28:44,093 --> 02:28:47,108
Mother!

1620
02:30:24,546 --> 02:30:27,597
Let's go or else he'll kill us!

1621
02:30:43,381 --> 02:30:44,491
Raju!

1622
02:31:39,242 --> 02:31:40,198
Don't kill us!

1623
02:31:40,299 --> 02:31:41,259
Forgive us.

1624
02:31:41,777 --> 02:31:45,745
I'm your dad-in-law.
Will you kill me, son?

1625
02:31:45,932 --> 02:31:47,484
No! Raju, no!

1626
02:31:48,754 --> 02:31:49,179
No!

1627
02:31:51,043 --> 02:31:52,907
I won't kill you.

1628
02:31:57,796 --> 02:31:59,447
He's so merciful!

1629
02:32:00,074 --> 02:32:02,859
After all he's my son-in-law.

1630
02:32:05,173 --> 02:32:06,062
Look up.

1631
02:32:16,255 --> 02:32:18,039
No! no.

1632
02:32:18,670 --> 02:32:22,355
These vultures will eat our flesh!

1633
02:32:22,638 --> 02:32:27,028
- Shoot us!
- Yes, kill us!

1634
02:32:27,378 --> 02:32:30,355
- For God's sake!
- I had pledged

1635
02:32:31,428 --> 02:32:34,150
that you will neither get
the flames of a cremation

1636
02:32:35,253 --> 02:32:37,119
nor the lap of mother earth!

1637
02:32:37,202 --> 02:32:38,846
- Raju No!
- No!

1638
02:32:38,870 --> 02:32:39,938
No!

1639
02:32:42,912 --> 02:32:48,204
Raju I gave false
evidence against your dad!

1640
02:32:48,595 --> 02:32:51,235
I had whipped him to death!

1641
02:32:51,490 --> 02:32:56,387
We are butchers!
Remove your revolver and kill me!

1642
02:32:56,859 --> 02:32:59,959
You are educated, sensible.
Why don't you kill us?

1643
02:33:00,250 --> 02:33:04,059
Villagers! We accept all our crimes.

1644
02:33:04,488 --> 02:33:07,854
Save us from the vultures.
We can't even walk!

1645
02:33:08,155 --> 02:33:12,452
Kill us! Wait! Where are you going?

1646
02:33:13,015 --> 02:33:16,022
On your goddess like mother's
forehead, I had written

1647
02:33:16,142 --> 02:33:20,739
your husband is a traitor!
You write on my forehead with bullets.

1648
02:33:21,197 --> 02:33:23,672
That I'm a dog, a pig, a swine!

1649
02:33:24,632 --> 02:33:27,572
- Stop!
- Don't leave us and go!

1650
02:34:00,767 --> 02:34:02,511
Guards!

1651
02:34:03,751 --> 02:34:05,185
General salute!

1652
02:34:08,281 --> 02:34:09,842
Gun salute!
